{"tid":263721,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"傻呢D傳統食物 真係唔係個個都鐘意食","createTime":"2017-05-30T09:05:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T10:35:08.000Z","uid":22589,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"150713f0eede1729393d1d6eebe9238361830320","tid":263721,"uid":22589,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T09:05:22.000Z","msg":"傻呢D傳統食物,真係唔係個個都鐘意食 <br />\n<br />\n傻的歷史悠久，在戰國時已經出現。 <br />\n<br />\n楚國詩人屈原投汨羅江自盡後， <br />\n<br />\n百姓為了防止其他人再做傻事 <br />\n<br />\n就用米整左隻唔係咁好食嘅食物, <br />\n<br />\n取名為&quot;傻&quot;,人每當食到呢種難食嘅食物 <br />\n<br />\n就會激發起&quot;去第二度食過D靚野&quot;嘅想法 <br />\n<br />\n從而打消自殺念頭 <br />\n<br />\n由於傻用米做,所以有後人將傻寫作糉,喻意為&quot;咪傻&quot;"},{"pid":"6355c59ce93c828e050c504ef826d8b473f1c992","tid":263721,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T09:08:15.000Z","msg":"樓主系傻既佼佼者"},{"pid":"7d8e9be127fbd005bd02d4d948d7f326eed6d505","tid":263721,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T09:09:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主系傻既佼佼者</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ad3b616d6f60b01f5ad178ff4c0f84e7ffa3cba","tid":263721,"uid":64884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T09:10:29.000Z","msg":"最尾又幾好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca7308734924673e0655bf3aa2133f1353cfb0e6","tid":263721,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T09:22:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"594914d4822cc19c979f2f44fb862b20582c0e14","tid":263721,"uid":14029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T09:25:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"548124475ff1ebe172d976eeb05c36e641fd821c","tid":263721,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T09:39:33.000Z","msg":"我比7分"}